net.visualcoding.ts3serverquery.event

Class TS3Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.visualcoding.ts3serverquery.event.TS3Event
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TS3ClientConnectedEvent, TS3ClientDisconnectedEvent, TS3ClientMovedEvent, TS3MessageEvent

    public abstract class TS3Event
extends Object
    This is an abstract class for TS3 events containing the basic fields that are present in all TS3 events.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Aldehir Rojas
